name: Lilith
description:
This was done with the purpose of being a tee design, but I decided to sell it as a print instead.

The text in the preview image will not be on the actual print.


- Printed on matte photo paper
- $5.00 shipping in the US, $15.00 for non-US
- Unsigned (unless you order the appropriate option)
- Should arrive about 2 weeks after ordering, longer for a signed print


Note: Signed prints by default have a signature on the front - special requests for back placement, etc. must be emailed to me prior to order.
